The '''Swordsmen Barracks''' is a building in the [[Levy Barracks]] category. It is used to recruit [[Swordsman|Swordsmen]].

== Production ==
The Swordsmen Barracks produces one [[Swordsman]] every 10 seconds. It consumes 10 [[Wheat]] and 8 [[Ore]] per cycle.

